snippet.title: Protocol Release Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/724490/Protocol/
Take on the role of the volunteer - a participant in the mission of the first contact, under the control of a soulless artificial intelligence.
Experience conspiracies, aliens, hackers, blockchains, family drama, cyberpunk, a bit of latex and domination... and also a lot of sparkling (and not very sparkling) humor. 
Have a nice day!
